criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  TMD as diagnosed according to the Research Diagnostic Criteria-TMD by a trained
             dentist;

          -  worst facial pain greater than 5 out of 10.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  prior surgery for TMD;

          -  life-threatening illnesses;

          -  conditions that would prevent participation in trial including consumption of Chinese
             herbs.
